WEBVTT

00:05:28.667 --> 00:05:30.351
The goals are very lofty,

00:05:30.375 --> 00:05:32.250
and very, very long-term,

00:05:33.167 --> 00:05:35.393
and none of them will be accomplished

00:05:35.417 --> 00:05:38.268
if they don't have
real steps along the way.

00:05:38.292 --> 00:05:39.684
It's like saying,

00:05:39.708 --> 00:05:43.750
"I'm going to run a marathon,
or a 5k, sometime in the future."

00:05:44.558 --> 00:05:48.559
No one is going to believe you
until they see you get off the couch,

00:05:48.583 --> 00:05:49.934
start training,

00:05:49.958 --> 00:05:52.792
putting in the miles every single day.

00:05:53.542 --> 00:05:56.184
CEOs need the same thing.

00:05:56.208 --> 00:06:00.393
They need concrete,
achievable, measurable goals,